formattedAddress: 333 Post St (btwn Post, Stockton, Geary & Powell St.)
location.crossStreet: btwn Post, Stockton, Geary & Powell St.

tip.text: Cozy little café in the west side of Kongsberg,  sells vintage stuffs and child-friendly.  Coffee's not so bad,  and may not be the best either but perfect place to chill on a rainy day.
Great coffee here! Pretty good Latte. Try the bacon chips and their craft beers.
Get a table in the A/C area by the window for good people watching.  Otah serves a good pair to Laksa.  Must combo!
Small seating but really good crepes.
